= A New Day in Germany

After the death of Hindenburg and the presidential election of 1934, it seems as if an era of history is closing. The worst years of political and economic crisis are over, and <span style="color: #7A3C00;">Nazism</span>'s days are numbered. Perhaps Germany will finally enter into a new era of genuine peace...
